{"tid":1389933,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"731全港臨時大罷工","createTime":"2019-07-31T04:29:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T04:42:49.000Z","uid":46526,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4ee3b1eb4dc67e5bd348218e641cd7577dc9095f","tid":1389933,"uid":46526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T04:29:43.000Z","msg":"參加方法：只要你係正常收工時間前<strong>拒絕</strong>繼續工作就等於參與行動<br />\n<br />\n鑒於731全港臨時大罷工將會<strong>癱瘓社會運作</strong>，請愛國愛港愛工作之人仕保持在工作崗位上。提早收工的行為在客觀上等於促進了罷工<strong>癱瘓社會運作</strong>的效果和目的；同時，法例亦沒有要求愛國愛港愛工作之人仕在極端惡劣天氣時<strong>必須</strong>提早收工。"},{"pid":"2127b9374dedc166f4c2a624ec0d62bb4603bb4b","tid":1389933,"uid":4060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T04:30:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"113e43ce5ca06c7958de2ca08105645c9e6afd5a","tid":1389933,"uid":187755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T04:42:49.000Z","msg":"#我係香港人 <br />\n#我會參與8月5日三罷 <br />\n#罷工罷市罷課"}]}